Text: It would have been nice if you'd mentioned you shouldn't install it and to use the cracked version - but no matter because the cracked version didn't actually want to add files as it said they wouldn't be converted (in my case these were mkv files). Plus the info in the bottom window said certain things weren't working properly and the programme should be reinstalled. It just doesn't seem to want to work. Don't know why but it doesn't. No KeyGen or seriels were included to attempt full installation even though the lot's clean.
